Package org.spongepowered.api.effect.sound

Class PitchModulation

java.lang.Object
org.spongepowered.api.effect.sound.PitchModulation
public final class PitchModulation extends Object
Represents a value to supply to Viewer.playSound(Sound, Vector3d) to modulate the pitch to a specified note.
